prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, a dynamic and humorous comic book panel featuring the couple from the reference photo, ID 9c3b8817-66fd-4e3d-b7a1-6b93df497ff3. The scene is a bright, sunny beach day. Lao Lao is the hero of the panel, striking a powerful superhero pose, one hand on her hip and the other pointing commandingly at the sky. She wears her light blue sweatshirt and black pants, reimagined as a superhero suit, and has a huge, confident smile. Jordan stands slightly behind her, wearing his brown hoodie and dark pants, looking on with an expression of comic admiration and surprise, holding two surfboards under one arm as if he's her trusty sidekick. The background is a vibrant beach with stylized waves, and in the distance, a giant, comical sandcastle shaped like a birthday cake with seashell candles. The whole scene is framed with classic comic book elements: bold black outlines, a dot pattern (Ben-Day dots) for shading, and a dramatic sunburst effect radiating from behind Lao Lao. A large, explosive comic book sound effect bubble near the couple says "POW!" or "ZAP!". Centered in the middle of the composition, the text "Happy Birthday, My Superhero!" is written in a fun, handwritten cursive script. Flat 2D artwork, bold and saturated colors typical of vintage comics.
